title: Any info about open seats in CSE and AIML in RR and EC campus before participating in 2nd round counselling??
content: What are the chances of getting a CSE or AIML in RR or EC campuses for a rank of 16xx. Did not attend the 1st round due to advanced exam (and in person counselling) and want to participate in 2nd round. Are there any vacancies in CSE or AIML?. Or the vancancies are only for ECE?. If any one has info, pls share it so that i can book tickets and prepare DDs. Need to travel from Delhi.

comments.body: They should release the seat matrix like 2-3 days before the actual day of councelling.
AIML seats where available till 16XX at RR in 1st round. So there is a good chance of getting AIML at RR or EC in 2nd round. But be ready for surprises.
